39064|"a growth, to have a history, and a development. Psychology in this sense"|FALSE
39064|"would be a dynamical, as opposed to the supposed statical, treatment of"|FALSE
39064|"ideas and concepts in logic. But it may be doubted how far it is well to"|FALSE
39064|"call this psychology: unless psychology deals with the contents of the"|FALSE
39064|"mental life, in their meaning and purpose, instead of, as seems proper,"|FALSE
