39064|"true or universal self-hood. Thus “psychological” here means the"|FALSE
39064|"recognition that the logical and the moral law is an autonomy: that it is"|FALSE
39064|"not given, but though necessary, necessary by the inward movement of the"|FALSE
39064|"mind. The metaphor of law is, in brief, misleading. For, according to a"|FALSE
