39064|"well-being, as part of an embracing system."|FALSE
39064|"There is probably another sense, however, in which psychology comes into"|FALSE
39064|"close relation with ethics. If we look on man as a microcosm, his inner"|FALSE
39064|"system will more or less reproduce the system of the larger world. The"|FALSE
39064|"older psychology used to distinguish an upper or superior order of"|FALSE
