39064|"To the strictly scientific psychologist, as has been noted—or to the"|FALSE
39064|"psychology which imitates optical and electrical science—ideas are only"|FALSE
39064|"psychical events: they are not ideas _of_ anything, relative, i.e. to"|FALSE
