39064|"the _prius_—or basis—of all mental life: the organisation of soul in body"|FALSE
39064|"and of body in soul. It is the process which historically has been"|FALSE
39064|"prepared in the evolution of animal life from those undifferentiated forms"|FALSE
39064|"where specialised organs are yet unknown, and which each individual has"|FALSE
39064|"further to realise and complete for himself, by learning to see and hear,"|FALSE
39064|"and use his limbs. At first, moreover, it begins from many separate"|FALSE
