39064|"This consolidation of inward life may be looked at either formally or"|FALSE
39064|"concretely. Under the first head, it means the growth of a central unity"|FALSE
39064|"of apperception. In the second case, it means a peculiar aggregate of"|FALSE
39064|"ideas and sentiments. There is growing up within him what we may call the"|FALSE
