39064|"likeness of an authoritative influence."|FALSE
39064|"The step by which the universality or unity of the self is realised in the"|FALSE
39064|"variety of its sensation is Habit. Habit gives us a definite"|FALSE
39064|"standing-ground in the flux of single impressions: it is the"|FALSE
