39064|"(ii.) Anomalies of Psychical Life."|FALSE
39064|"Psychology, as we have seen, goes for information regarding the earlier"|FALSE
39064|"stages of mental growth to the child and the animal,—perhaps also to the"|FALSE
39064|"savage. So too sociology founds certain conclusions upon the observations"|FALSE
