39064|"aim is to get worship, to be recognised as the best in his little sphere."|FALSE
39064|"But with the growth of the trading spirit his character changes: he"|FALSE
39064|"becomes the mere capitalist, is denationalised, has no definite work and"|FALSE
39064|"can claim no individualised function. Money now measures all things: it is"|FALSE
39064|"the sole ultimate reality. It transforms everything into a relation of"|FALSE
39064|"contract: even vengeance is equated in terms of money. Its motto is, The"|FALSE
39064|"Exchanges must be honoured, though honour and morality may go to the dogs."|FALSE
39064|"So far as it is concerned, there is no nation, but a federation of"|FALSE
39064|"shopkeepers. Such an one is the _bourgeois_ (the _Bürger_, as distinct"|FALSE
