39064|"§ 403. The feeling or sentient individual is the simple “ideality” or"|FALSE
39064|"subjective side of sensation. What it has to do, therefore, is to raise"|FALSE
39064|"its substantiality, its merely virtual filling-up, to the character of"|FALSE
