39064|"§ 422. The proximate _truth_ of perception is that it is the object which"|FALSE
39064|"is an _appearance_, and that the object’s reflection in self is on the"|FALSE
39064|"contrary a self-subsistent inward and universal. The consciousness of such"|FALSE
