39064|"(b) Self-consciousness(130)."|FALSE
39064|"§ 424. _Self-consciousness_ is the truth of consciousness: the latter is a"|FALSE
39064|"consequence of the former, all consciousness of an other object being as a"|FALSE
39064|"matter of fact also self-consciousness. The object is my idea: I am aware"|FALSE
