39064|"(α) Appetite or Instinctive Desire(131)."|FALSE
39064|"§ 426. Self-consciousness, in its immediacy, is a singular, and a desire"|FALSE
39064|"(appetite),—the contradiction implied in its abstraction which should yet"|FALSE
39064|"be objective,—or in its immediacy which has the shape of an external"|FALSE
