39064|"(β) Self-consciousness Recognitive(132)."|FALSE
39064|"§ 430. Here there is a self-consciousness for a self-consciousness, at"|FALSE
39064|"first immediately as one of two things for another. In that other as ego I"|FALSE
39064|"behold myself, and yet also an immediately existing object, another ego"|FALSE
