39064|"§ 441. The soul is finite, so far as its features are immediate or"|FALSE
39064|"con-natural. Consciousness is finite, in so far as it has an object. Mind"|FALSE
39064|"is finite, in so far as, though it no longer has an object, it has a mode"|FALSE
