39064|"The _positive_ element in laws concerns only their form of _publicity_ and"|FALSE
39064|"_authority_—which makes it possible for them to be known by all in a"|FALSE
39064|"customary and external way. Their content _per se_ may be reasonable—or it"|FALSE
