39064|"§ 545. The final aspect of the state is to appear in immediate actuality"|FALSE
39064|"as a single nation marked by physical conditions. As a single individual"|FALSE
39064|"it is exclusive against other like individuals. In their mutual relations,"|FALSE
39064|"waywardness and chance have a place; for each person in the aggregate is"|FALSE
