39064|"patriotic sacrifice on the part of these individuals of this natural and"|FALSE
39064|"particular existence,—so making nugatory the nugatoriness that confronts"|FALSE
39064|"it."|FALSE
39064|"β. External Public Law(168)."|FALSE
39064|"§ 547. In the game of war the independence of States is at stake. In one"|FALSE
39064|"case the result may be the mutual recognition of free national"|FALSE
