39064|"the universal will steps onward over its property for the time being, as"|FALSE
39064|"over a special grade, and then delivers it over to its chance and doom."|FALSE
39064|"§ 551. To such extent as this business of actuality appears as an action,"|FALSE
39064|"and therefore as a work of _individuals_, these individuals, as regards"|FALSE
39064|"the substantial issue of their labour, are _instruments_, and their"|FALSE
39064|"subjectivity, which is what is peculiar to them, is the empty form of"|FALSE
39064|"activity. What they personally have gained therefore through the"|FALSE
39064|"individual share they took in the substantial business (prepared and"|FALSE
