39064|"§ 552. The national spirit contains nature-necessity, and stands in"|FALSE
39064|"external existence (§ 423): the ethical substance, potentially infinite,"|FALSE
39064|"is actually a particular and limited substance (§§ 549, 550); on its"|FALSE
39064|"subjective side it labours under contingency, in the shape of its"|FALSE
