39064|"subjective liberty (§ 503 note, § 513, &c.). The truth which should be"|FALSE
39064|"immanent in the state, should knit it together and control it, he, for"|FALSE
39064|"these reasons, got hold of only the form of thought-out truth, of"|FALSE
