39064|"orthodoxy. It had too little of God in it for the former; too much for the"|FALSE
39064|"latter."|FALSE
39064|"The charge of _Atheism_, which used often to be brought against philosophy"|FALSE
39064|"(that it has _too little_ of God), has grown rare: the more wide-spread"|FALSE
39064|"grows the charge of Pantheism, that it has _too much_ of him:—so much so,"|FALSE
